"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?20/28/20938/contributors\">",
"     Bradley P Knight, MD, FACC",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
